<i>¡Ayúdenme!</i>

680
00:47:11.195 --> 00:47:12.162
<i>¡Auxilio!</i>

681
00:47:13.063 --> 00:47:14.398
<i>¡Necesito ayuda!</i>

682
00:47:14.965 --> 00:47:16.133
<i>¡Ayúdenme!</i>

683
00:47:17.334 --> 00:47:18.468
<i>¡Auxilio!</i>

684
00:47:19.570 --> 00:47:20.404
Mike.

685
